data.description: Beautiful home featuring 3 beds, 2 fully updated baths, open concept, two living areas, nice backsplash in kitchen with nice counters and beautiful modern sink, neutral paint colors in and out, nice size yard with plenty of space. Minutes away from I10, Northstar Mall, and major retail stores, NE schools, and more.  New sod will be added to front yard prior to closing giving it the final touch. Come by and take a look!
